Problems to solve
- redirects and protocol switches, 404s
- don't re-request up-to-date content
- truncating content
- html values
- use Rufus for in-server refresh worker
  makes the app more easily deployed to platforms like Heroku
- storing raw feed XML in the filesystem prevents deploying to Heroku,
  consider storing it in the DB or using something like S3.
- favicons
- error logging

